-- Goldman Sachs, Morgan Stanley shares slide
-- 
-- Tue Oct 28, 2008 11:20am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/28/us-markets-stocks-goldmanmorgan-idUSTRE49R5K120081028

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of investment banks Goldman Sachs Group Inc ( GS.N ) and Morgan Stanley ( MS.N ) fell sharply on Tuesday in a slide that briefly halted an attempted recovery of the overall U.S. stock market. 

 Goldman shares fell 10.1 percent to $83.58 in morning trade, while Morgan shares slid 19.8 percent to $11.01. (Reporting by  Herbert Lash ; Editing by  James Dalgleish )